  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Palliative cancer patients,

          -  life expectancy between 3 and 12 months,

          -  Karnofsky status equally or above 60,

          -  pain score equal or below 3 on numerical rating scale (0-10),

          -  cognitive function intact
